{
  "stem": "20142.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a former officer of the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when they were building the-- when they were building Majdanek and all the camps, they took the former Jews who were officers of Polish army, and made them the barracks leaders, or kapos, or even higher hierarchy.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he is somehow took interest in my looks, and he start asking me question.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was very, very friendly with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He permitted me to conduct certain services like sweeping the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And for this, you were getting additional soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was of great help to anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There are many people who envy me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't ask for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He just came to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I don't know why such thing happen, but it did happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it help me to somehow to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, every Sunday, I went-- there was experience of hanging people for people-- everybody had to stay on [GERMAN] place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a routine life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You had to work and do certain work outside of the barracks, and you were counted and you were walking out in columns and coming in in columns.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If there were greater number of people that walk out and the group leader had to announce how many he has, then the last two people-- had to be always even number.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If you walk out with 400, you had to come back with 400.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If all a sudden somebody from any other groups got attached just to get back to the camp, and he was 402, those last two people were taken and killed on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Or they were using another tactics.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That they took the numbers, and they called these people on Sunday, and they hang them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was quite one incident good I remember quite well.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
